      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>Should you need to export a .RIB file manually, you can use the Maya File Menu &gt; Export All &gt; RIB</p><p>Note that to create a frame rendering scene file, the option for As Archive must be <em>off</em> (unchecked) or the export will omit the required rendering options.</p><p> </p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" confluence-query-params=\"effects=drop-shadow\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543164/rfm_RIBExport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431593514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;effects=drop-shadow\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543164/rfm_RIBExport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431593514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544543176\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfm_RIBExport.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544543164\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c163410e-a6cf-491b-9ade-d06c97db20ee\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p>"
